section.def:
Chairman
                (主席) means the Chairman for the time being of the
            Executive Committee;

constitution
                (章程) means the constitution of the Society for
            the time being in force;

paragraph.content:
all investments and movable property vested in or belonging to or held for or
                on behalf of or in trust for the existing society shall be transferred to vest in,
                belong to or be held for or on behalf of or in trust for the Society;
